{"tid":1488133,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"何韻詩及其支持者 及有正評佢20000分嘅巴絲打入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-19T14:08:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-21T14:51:44.000Z","uid":7971,"like":67,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"f90c1ec6113108ce2c509365c3c18e38006de9dd","tid":1488133,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/19/XhiGnB.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F19%2FXhiGnB.jpeg&h=82c23a74&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/08/19/Ps4eJ3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F08%2F19%2FPs4eJ3.jpeg&h=3f1f24f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n/<br />\n<br />\n真心一問 其實我哋贏咗咩？<br />\n五大訴求 一個都無贏過<br />\n<br />\n係未以後 只要我哋見到<br />\n泛民議員、學者、知名人士<br />\n就算佢哋發表嘅言論有問題<br />\n但只要佢哋係_____ 做過______ (eg坐過監/放棄支那市場)<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">就唔可以敬告？唔可以監察？唔可以批評？<br />\n係未提出意見 就係分化？</span><br />\n如果咁都唔係光環論調 請問什麼先係光環？<br />\n<br />\n我真心誠懇一句<br />\n知名人士 都會錯 佢哋都係人<br />\n依場運動嘅仲行到依一步 係因為<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">「我哋所有行動同發言，唔係基於社經地位、職業身分、年齡、性別，而係大家都基於相近嘅價值觀，一齊去爭取，可行就推，可行就做。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">唔好再張仼何人放上神台 <br />\n都唔好覺得提出意見就係批評</span><br />\n就好似我早幾日 都太激動之下 <br />\n開咗一個語氣唔好 令大家有爭論嘅post<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\">所以我懇請大家 真係要保持獨立思考</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">因為我哋仲係<br />\n輸梗5:0 <br />\n輸咗800位手足 <br />\n輸咗6位殉道者 <br />\n輸咗1位女生嘅眼</div>"},{"pid":"7cb638d620f0d9d0a550d86d6ee0cc31aa7e85a0","tid":1488133,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a9b367a2e58b45e6f8c553b54418fbc2000a500","tid":1488133,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:09:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9f64e210db6a00ae4f361b955b882b48e544d6bb","tid":1488133,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:09:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"862ecb3e91f59ccf5632e94d9663842dc65f15db","tid":1488133,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:09:55.000Z","msg":"（整合） 818之後仲有行動㗎我地！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1487938\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1487938</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n普教中！！！救下香港嘅下一代！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1475548\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1475548</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"beaf2dbde2579a0d2af15e0dac4bc8afa6ababaa","tid":1488133,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:10:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"431d00981108e648cb380a37beab4e2e6839b651","tid":1488133,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:10:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9d117f14ef6120972a86206a6c8caab59657ff5","tid":1488133,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:11:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20263f7492f539d091013041b49b0681539f6d67","tid":1488133,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:12:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e660007c5d9f3bfed5823040a6f8ea91ce731888","tid":1488133,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:13:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed4d70e44909631871513217447313d54cacb163","tid":1488133,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:13:59.000Z","msg":"如果內文都無睇 就負評 <br />\n我無言以對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc6fbedfdbdb6874434ed7cf28b068897701f9af","tid":1488133,"uid":294380,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T14:14:03.000Z","msg":"1. 七一嗰晚，發夢見到佢同明哥一齊係立會外面，等到入面d手足搞掂先一齊走<br />\n2. 元朗嗰日又話搞流動簽名會<br />\n公眾人物嚟講算係好勇，擺到明同政府作對<br />\n3. 而且HOCC隨時返加拿大都得，仲出嚟搞咁多，真心為香港 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}